&lt;p&gt;The Arduino based Social Board is an analogue social network for a close
knit group of friends.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It's a design object that tells you at a glance how your friends are
feeling and what they are up to for the night, making a digital
information pleasantly physical.&lt;/p&gt;
